  "title": "Sighs",
  "sourceFile": "Waste_notes/sighs_N.htm",
  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>Sighs,\n        short and ...</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>Cf. Inferno IV, 25-27: </p>\n<p>Quivi, secondo che per ascolatre,<br/>\n        non avea piante mai che di sospiri<br/>\n        che l'aura eterna facevan tremare. <a href=\"quivi_T.htm\"><img alt=\"click here for translation\" src=\"../images/T.gif\"/></a> <br/>\n        [Eliot's note]</p>\n<p>In Limbo, the first circle of hell, Dante has found\n        the virtuous heathens, who lived before Christianity and\n        are, therefore, eternally unable to achieve their desire\n        of seeing God (NA).</p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"inferno_iv.htm\">Dante,\n                Inferno IV</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "Sighs, short and ... Cf. Inferno IV, 25-27: Quivi, secondo che per ascolatre, non avea piante mai che di sospiri che l'aura eterna facevan tremare. [Eliot's note] In Limbo, the first circle of hell, Dante has found the virtuous heathens, who lived before Christianity and are, therefore, eternally unable to achieve their desire of seeing God (NA). reference topics Dante, Inferno IV back to \"The Waste Land\"",
